positive.review: Jezus christ superstar, this is again my fall back game. Tried fm26, what a utter piece of crap. Lifeless simulation. Just had to go back to this one.

One of the best FM's!  9/10!!!
Only rival to this one is FM24, which is very similar, yet slightly different.
Stay clear of FM26 - play '22 or '24 until the release of FM27 or perhaps FM28.
I TRIED TO FIND THIS GAME FOR 3 YEARS AND FIANALLY FOUND MY OLD ACC
Very good compared to the car crash that is fm26 how did we go fm 22 fm 23 and fm24 being good to fm 26 being terrible 22 is good in 2025 still despite being old
